  "description": "<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><strong>Item specifics:</strong></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Condition:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">New</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Type:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Blow off Valve</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Manufacturer Part Number:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">FE455810</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Brand:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">FAPO MOTO</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Manufacturer Warranty:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">1 Year</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Finish:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Polished</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Model:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">50MM</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Fitment Type:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Direct Replacement</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Color:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Silver</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Universal Fitment:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Yes</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Diameter:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">50mm (2\")</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><br>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Material:</span><span style=\"white-space:pre;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Aluminium</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br>\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Application: </span></strong> \n\t</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Can be used when installing Tial Q &amp; QR 50mm blow off valve, or Tial style 50mm dump valves</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> </span> \n\t</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Features:</span></strong> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\">\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-This flange is designed to be welded onto your intake pipe work, It makes installing an aftermarket blow off valve much easier</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-This is not a Tial product, we are just stating it can be used with some of their valves</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-These work really easily welding to 2.25\" to 2.5\" piping</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-Precise radius for easy welding</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-No more grinding or modification</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">-1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</span><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Package Included:</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">1x Flange. (100% Brand New Never Used Or Installed)</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> </span> \n</p>\n\t</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Technical Specifications:</span></strong> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:\" font-size:18.6667px=\"\"> <span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Diameter: 50mm (2\") </span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Material: Aluminium</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">Finish: Polished</span> \n\t</div>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<br>\n\t</p>",
